1
00:00:00,083 --> 00:00:02,791
I only remember someone
standing here with a sword

2
00:00:03,291 --> 00:00:04,458
I looked at him from above

3
00:00:05,291 --> 00:00:06,750
He was standing
here, in this spot

4
00:00:08,541 --> 00:00:10,041
That's what I remember

5
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:11,916
It never leaves my mind

6
00:00:13,916 --> 00:00:15,625
Interviewer: What
did that man look like?

7
00:00:15,625 --> 00:00:16,875
He was huge and masked;
you couldn't see his face

8
00:00:18,333 --> 00:00:22,625
Even his hands were
hidden because of tattoos

9
00:00:22,958 --> 00:00:24,291
So no one would recognize him
